author: lgo
msg: Prepare the python tests to be run in parallel:
Create the temp folders upfront instead of checking again for each test case.
This avoids nasty problems when two tests run in parallel try to create those
(copy_repos): remove another now obsolete check for the temp folder
(setup_pristine_repository): create the temp folders if needed.
(make_repo_and_wc): don't check for those folders on each startup, they're
supposed to be there by now.
